WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Welcome to British English Academy C2-M01: Identity, goals and learner profile. Learners practise shape nuanced arguments through introductions, routines, aspirations, personal information. The teacher models precision, ambiguity and nuance, introduces vocabulary such as personal details, goals, classroom objects, numbers, dates, then learners complete quiz, evidence upload and reflection.
